channel.title: Need help with a private server help is appreciated
channel.description:
NOTE: Everytime i post on here i guess i never post in the right place, so if somone would be kind and let me know if i can post this thread here please do! :)
hi there, i am new to making and coding rsps, i was wondering if anyone would help me with one, im looking to spend all my time on this even as a job i guess.
my msn is ftw.2012@yahoo.ca if anyone could help add me please thanks.
i dont know much so if your willing to teach me, im willing to listen, and do all that is asked. please try to be above most people so i can learn from more of an expert, but atm anyone will do, im joansin for a server and getting started on it.
i need any help i can get my msn is ftw.2012@yahoo.ca Thanks.
